<item>
            <title>[LU-5864] New static analysis issues in lfs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5864</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In commit &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/9383&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;979203503af2f77d51bcf27375a1a09f5f28a4a3&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4665&quot; title=&quot;utils: lfs setstripe to specify OSTs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4665&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4665&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; utils: lfs setstripe to specify OSTs) was introduced suspicious dereference of pointer &apos;ptr&apos; before NULL check at line 704.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="27460">LU-5864</key>
            <summary>New static analysis issues in lfs</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=11303&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
